text: Portengen is a hamlet in the Dutch province of Utrecht. It is located in the municipality of Stichtse Vecht, northeast of Kockengen. Portengen was a separate municipality from 1818 to 1857, when it was merged with Breukelen- Nijenrode. ==References== Category:Populated places in Utrecht (province) Category:Former municipalities of Utrecht (province) Category:Stichtse Vecht Category:1818 establishments in the Netherlands
